reviews.reviewText: Beautiful deep colors and great material. I used this on my office desk under my keyboard to pull the color pattern in the room together. Love this runner

reviews.reviewText: These are so pretty and the color and pattern will do a good job hiding stains.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Bright white napkins that are easy to dress up
reviews.reviewText: These are nice and thick. They came folded. The stains came off when washed with some bleach and they look as good as new! They will have to be lightly ironed for the next use.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love the rich colors
reviews.reviewText: This is beautiful. Love the colors - photo was accurate. I was able to get matching napkins as wel

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I really like these. I was worried it would be wrinkled after being washed but it was really good. I bought these to use on a daily basis instead of paper towels. I like them so much I ordered 2 more.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 25, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Time will tell
reviews.reviewText: I wish these were wrinkle-free but they aren’t. They aren’t terrible but for everyday use, I can easily forgo the iron.They are an attractive addition to our table. I hope they don’t fade too fast.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 9, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Cotton embroidered vibrant colors. Just as described. Highly recommendI got it to protect the top of the credenza that was getting destroyed by the Sun.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very pretty napkin, the finish work was well done.
reviews.reviewText: The napkins arrived quickly, were pretty and finished well.
